[00:12.85]「  」
[00:12.86]Goodbye to you my trusted friend
[00:15.98]「至交老友 向你道声离别」
[00:18.45]We've known each other since we were nine or ten
[00:22.68]「我们相识于天真烂漫的童年」
[00:23.83]Together we've climbed hills and trees
[00:27.16]「青山流水间留下我们的足迹」
[00:29.60]Learned of love and ABC's
[00:32.28]「共同经历着青涩无忧的爱」
[00:32.29]Skinned our hearts and skinned our knees
[00:34.78]「这段青春为盟的年少轻狂」
[00:34.79]Goodbye my friend it's hard to die
[00:37.90]「再见了 老友 这声珍重实难开口」
[00:40.19][01:40.20][02:53.82]When all the birds are singing in the sky
[00:44.82][01:45.11][02:58.05]「当群鸟在天际欢呼高唱」
[00:45.97]Now that spring is in the air
