[00:51.47]Pretty girls are everywhere
[00:55.12]「随处可见漂亮的女孩」
[00:56.87]Think of me and I'll be there
[00:59.60]「想起我 我便与你同在」
[00:59.61][01:59.63][02:10.59][03:13.25][03:24.26][03:35.13][03:46.00][03:56.91]We had joy we had fun we had seasons in the sun
[01:05.03][02:05.08][02:16.03][03:18.65][03:29.59][03:40.46][03:51.39]「我们曾肆意欢笑 也曾纵情享乐」
[01:05.04][03:18.66]But the hills that we climbed were just seasons out of time
[01:10.81][03:24.25]「我们曾共享过无虑的阳光季节」
[01:12.89]Goodbye Papa please pray for me
[01:15.87]「再见了 老爸 请为我祈祷」
[01:18.28]I was the black sheep of the family
[01:22.84]「我曾是家里的害群之马」
[01:23.82]You tried to teach me right from wrong
[01:26.99]「你费尽心思教我辨别是非对错」
[01:29.61]Too much wine and too much song
[01:32.36]「我却沉溺于歌酒狂欢」
[01:32.37]Wonder how I got along
[01:34.78]「真不知道我是如何度过那些时光」
[01:34.79]Goodbye Papa it's hard to die
[01:37.97]「再见了 老爸 告别真的很难启齿」
[01:45.69][02:59.24]Now that the spring is in the air
[01:51.44]Little children everywhere
[01:54.81]「到处都是天真的稚嫩孩童」
[01:56.83]When you see them I'll be there
[01:59.62]「当你看到这一切 我便与你同在」
[02:05.09][02:16.04][03:29.60][03:40.47][03:51.40]But the wine and the song like the seasons have all gone
[02:10.58][02:21.38][03:35.12][03:45.99][03:56.90]「便如这更迭的四季悄然逝去」
[02:22.60]Yeah yeah
[02:26.63]Goodbye Michelle my little one
[02:29.76]「再见了 米歇尔 我的小情人」
